{"pv40:0.1":"Petavatthu ","pv40:0.2":"Mahavagga ","pv40:0.3":"5. Ucchupetavatthu ","pv40:1.1":"“Idam mama ucchuvanam mahantam, ","pv40:1.2":"Nibbattati punnaphalam anappakam; ","pv40:1.3":"Tam dani me na paribhogameti, ","pv40:1.4":"Acikkha bhante kissa ayam vipako. ","pv40:2.1":"Hannami khajjami ca vayamami, ","pv40:2.2":"Parisakkami paribhunjitum kinci; ","pv40:2.3":"Svaham chinnathamo kapano lalapami, ","pv40:2.4":"Kissa kammassa ayam vipako. ","pv40:3.1":"Vighato caham paripatami chamayam, ","pv40:3.2":"Parivattami varicarova ghamme; ","pv40:3.3":"Rudato ca me assuka niggalanti, ","pv40:3.4":"Acikkha bhante kissa ayam vipako. ","pv40:4.1":"Chato kilanto ca pipasito ca, ","pv40:4.2":"Santassito satasukham na vinde; ","pv40:4.3":"Pucchami tam etamattham bhadante, ","pv40:4.4":"Katham nu ucchuparibhogam labheyyan”ti. ","pv40:5.1":"“Pure tuvam kammamakasi attana, ","pv40:5.2":"Manussabhuto purimaya jatiya; ","pv40:5.3":"Ahanca tam etamattham vadami, ","pv40:5.4":"Sutvana tvam etamattham vijana. ","pv40:6.1":"Ucchum tuvam khadamano payato, ","pv40:6.2":"Puriso ca te pitthito anvagacchi; ","pv40:6.3":"So ca tam paccasanto kathesi, ","pv40:6.4":"Tassa tuvam na kinci alapittha. ","pv40:7.1":"So ca tam abhanantam ayaci, ","pv40:7.2":"‘Dehayya ucchun’ti ca tam avoca; ","pv40:7.3":"Tassa tuvam pitthito ucchum adasi, ","pv40:7.4":"Tassetam kammassa ayam vipako. ","pv40:8.1":"Ingha tvam gantvana pitthito ganheyyasi, ","pv40:8.2":"Gahetvana tam khadassu yavadattham; ","pv40:8.3":"Teneva tvam attamano bhavissasi, ","pv40:8.4":"Hattho cudaggo ca pamodito ca”ti. ","pv40:9.1":"Gantvana so pitthito aggahesi, ","pv40:9.2":"Gahetvana tam khadi yavadattham; ","pv40:9.3":"Teneva so attamano ahosi, ","pv40:9.4":"Hattho cudaggo ca pamodito cati. ","pv40:10.1":"Ucchupetavatthu pancamam. "}